@page "/"

<PageTitle>My URL Shortener Admin</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to My URL Shortener Admin Panel 🚀</h1>
<div>
    <p>
        This platform is designed to help you <b>manage and shorten long URLs easily</b>. 
        If you have a long and complex URL, you can convert it into a <b>custom short link</b> 
        that is easy to remember and share.
    </p>

    <h3>How Does It Work?</h3>
    <p>
        Imagine you have a long URL like:  
        🔗 <i>https://website.com/products/category/sub-category/item-details?ref=12345667882323791</i>
    </p>
    <p>
        With our URL shortener, you can transform it into a Friendly link like:  
        ✅ <b>https://alejandralara.com/Products</b>
    </p>

    <h3>Features 🎯</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>🛠️ <b>URL Manager</b> – Create, edit, and archive your custom short URLs.</li>
        <li>📊 <b>Click Analytics</b> – Track how many times your shortened links have been accessed.</li>
        <li>🔗 <b>Custom Short Links</b> – Personalize your URLs instead of using random codes.</li>
        <li>🎨 <b>User-Friendly Interface</b> – Simple and intuitive design for easy navigation.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        To get started, go to the <b>"URL Manager"</b> tab to create and manage your links.
        If you want to track the performance of your shortened URLs, check the <b>"Click Statistics"</b> section.
    </p>

    <p>Enjoy a smarter way to share links! 🚀</p>

    <div style="align-content: right;"><img class="mainLogo" src="/images/TinyBlazorAdmin.png" /></div>
</div>
